subject: Collaboration request
description_text:
Good morning guys, I wanted to review your products! Would you like to
start a collaboration? I am Mario Cimarelli on social Cima_89. I have a
YouTube@Cima_89 channel, a Twitch channel @cima_89, and an Instagram
channel @cima89. I don't leave you the links so as not to end up in spam!
Waiting for your kind feedback, I wish you a good day and good work.
